<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-0 pb-10 space-y-6" dir="rtl">
  <header class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-emerald-200/70 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50/90 via-white to-slate-50 shadow-sm">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_70%_50%_at_0%_0%,rgba(16,185,129,0.08),transparent)] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4 p-5 sm:p-7">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-600 to-teal-700 text-white shadow-md">
          <i class="fas fa-exchange-alt text-xl"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="min-w-0">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-700 mb-0.5">صرف وربح</p>
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">فرق التصريف</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1 leading-relaxed">سجّل عمليات التصريف واحسب الربح من فرق السعر تلقائياً.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="/dashboard" class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm transition hover:border-emerald-200 hover:bg-emerald-50">
        <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-xs opacity-70"></i>
        لوحة التحكم
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-indigo-100 bg-indigo-50/50 p-4 sm:p-5 text-sm text-indigo-900 leading-relaxed">
    <p class="font-bold text-indigo-950 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><i class="fas fa-calculator text-indigo-600"></i> طريقة الحساب</p>
    <p>أدخل <strong>المبلغ المراد تصريفه (بالدولار)</strong>، ثم <strong>السعر المثبت</strong> (السعر الذي تحاسب عليه)، ثم <strong>سعر الشراء</strong> (السعر الذي صرفت به فعلياً). الربح = المبلغ × (سعر الشراء − السعر المثبت) ÷ سعر الشراء.</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-indigo-800/90">مثال: 1000$ × (46 − 45) ÷ 46 ≈ 21.74$ ربح</p>
  </div>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/90 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
    <div class="border-b border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/80 px-5 py-4">
      <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-slate-900">تسجيل حدث جديد</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="p-5 sm:p-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-1.5">
          <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">الدورة المالية (اختياري)</label>
          <select id="fxCycleId" class="w-full rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm transition focus:border-indigo-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/15">
            <option value="">— عام —</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1.5">
          <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">العملة</label>
          <select id="fxCurrency" class="w-full rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/15">
            <option value="TRY">TRY</option>
            <option value="SYP">SYP</option>
            <option value="EGP">EGP</option>
            <option value="EUR">EUR</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1.5">
          <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">المبلغ المراد تصريفه (بالدولار)</label>
          <input type="number" id="fxAmountUsd" step="0.01" min="0" class="w-full rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-mono tabular-nums focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/15" placeholder="1000">
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1.5">
          <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">السعر المثبت (وحدة/USD)</label>
          <input type="number" id="fxInternal" step="0.0001" min="0" class="w-full rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-mono tabular-nums focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/15" placeholder="45">
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1.5">
          <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">سعر الشراء الفعلي (وحدة/USD)</label>
          <input type="number" id="fxSettlement" step="0.0001" min="0" class="w-full rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-mono tabular-nums focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/15" placeholder="46">
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1.5">
          <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">الجهة (اختياري)</label>
          <select id="fxEntityType" class="w-full rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/15">
            <option value="">— لا يوجد —</option>
            <option value="transfer_company">شركة تحويل</option>
            <option value="fund">صندوق</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1.5">
          <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">معرّف الكيان</label>
          <input type="number" id="fxEntityId" min="0" class="w-full rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/15" placeholder="رقم">
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-1.5">
          <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">ملاحظات</label>
          <input type="text" id="fxNotes" class="w-full rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/15" placeholder="اختياري">
        </div>
      </div>
      <p id="fxPreview" class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-4 min-h-[1.25rem]"></p>
      <button type="button" id="fxSubmit" class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-md shadow-indigo-600/20 hover:bg-indigo-700 active:scale-[0.99] transition">حفظ</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-slate-200/80 text-slate-700"><i class="fas fa-list-ul text-sm"></i></span>
      السجل
    </h3>
    <div id="fxList" class="space-y-2 text-sm rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/40 p-3 min-h-[3rem]"></div>
  </section>
</div>
